# Absinthe 2.x Release Notes

## Version 2.0.4
- Added iPad 2,4 support
- Fixed lockdown error -5 with improved error handling

## Version 2.0.3
- Updated device detection and communication code
- Improved stability on various device models

## Version 2.0.2
- Added support for iPhone 4 (GSM) 5.1.1b build 9B208

## Version 2.0.1
- Fixed a possible hang in certain jailbreak scenarios

## Version 2.0
- First public release
- Support for iOS 5.1.1 devices
- Cross-platform support (macOS, Windows, Linux)
- GUI application for simplified user experience
